---

<BaseLayout>
  <section>
    <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-24 lg:pt-48">
      <div class="overflow-hidden">
        <Text
          tag="h1"
          variant="displayMD"
          data-aos="fade-down"
          data-aos-duration="1500"
          class="dark:text-white xl:text-6xl tracking-tight font-medium text-black text-balance"
        >
          TreonStudio is a creative studio based in Yogyakarta that specializes in creating beautiful and simple brands for businesses that customers remember.
        </Text>
      </div>
      <Image
        width={1000}
        height={2000}
        src={Avatar}
        alt="#_"
        class="w-full aspect-[8/6] mt-4 object-cover object-center"
      />

      <Text
        tag="p"
        variant="textXL"
        class="text-base-500 dark:text-base-300 lg:text-balance mt-12 md:max-w-2xl"
      >
        At TreonStudio, we craft thoughtful, elegant design solutions that leave a lasting impression. Based in Yogyakarta, our studio specializes in distilling brands to their essence—creating simple, memorable identities that connect with audiences effortlessly.
        <br />
        <br />
        With a deep appreciation for clarity, balance, and craftsmanship, we blend strategy and aesthetics to build brands that feel both timeless and distinctive. Our work is rooted in precision and purpose, ensuring that every design is not only visually compelling but also meaningful and functional.
        <br />
        <br />
        We believe that great design is an experience—one that speaks without excess, resonates without noise, and endures beyond trends. Through a refined and intentional approach, we shape identities that stand out in a world of fleeting impressions.
        impressions.
      </Text>
    </Wrapper>
  </section>
  <section>
    <Wrapper class="pt-12 pb-24">
      <div class="overflow-hidden">
        <Text
          tag="h3"
          variant="displayXL"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-duration="1000"
          class="dark:text-white text-base-900 font-medium tracking-tighter"
        >
          Awards &amp; honors
        </Text>
      </div>
      <ul
        role="list"
        class="flex flex-col divide-y divide-base-200 dark:divide-base-800 border-t border-base-200 dark:border-base-800 mt-4"
      >
        {
          awards.map((award) => (
            <li class=" items-baseline flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:justify-between py-4  sticky top-20 z-10 bg-base-100 dark:bg-base-900">
              <div>
                <Text
                  tag="h3"
                  variant="displayMD"
                  class="dark:text-white text-base-900 font-medium tracking-tighter "
                >
                  {award.name}
                </Text>
                <Text
                  tag="p"
                  variant="textXL"
                  class="text-base-500 dark:text-base-400"
                >
                  {award.award}
                </Text>
                <Text
                  tag="p"
                  variant="textXL"
                  class="text-base-500 dark:text-base-500"
                >
                  {award.organization}
                </Text>
                <Text
                  tag="p"
                  variant="textXL"
                  class="text-base-500 dark:text-base-600"
                >
                  {award.project}
                </Text>
              </div>
              <a href={award.url} title={award.name} aria-label={award.name}>
                <svg
                  class="size-8 lg:size-14 dark:text-white text-base-900"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 256 256"
                >
                  <path d="M200,64V168a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V83.31L69.66,197.66a8,8,0,0,1-11.32-11.32L172.69,72H88a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H192A8,8,0,0,1,200,64Z" />
                </svg>
              </a>
            </li>
          ))
        }
      </ul>
    </Wrapper>
  </section>
  <LogoCloud />
  <section>
    <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-24">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <Text
          tag="h3"
          variant="displayXL"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-duration="1000"
          class="dark:text-white text-base-900 font-medium tracking-tighter"
          >the
          <br />
          team
        </Text>

        <div
          class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-y-12 gap-2 lg:col-span-3"
        >
          {
            teamMembers.map((member, index) => (
              <div class="flex flex-col ">
                <Image
                  width={500}
                  height={500}
                  src={member.image}
                  alt={member.name}
                  class="w-full  object-cover"
                />
                <div class="mt-2">
                  <Text
                    tag="h3"
                    variant="textBase"
                    class="leading-6 text-base-900 dark:text-white"
                  >
                    (0{index + 1}) {member.name}
                  </Text>
                  <Text
                    tag="p"
                    variant="textSM"
                    class="text-base-500 dark:text-base-400"
                  >
                    {member.role}
                  </Text>
                  <Text
                    tag="p"
                    variant="textSM"
                    class="text-base-500 mt-4 dark:text-base-400"
                  >
                    {member.bio}
                  </Text>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </Wrapper>
    <section>
      <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-12">
        <Text
          tag="h3"
          variant="displayMD"
          class="dark:text-white xl:text-7xl tracking-tight font-medium text-black text-balance lg:col-span-3"
        >
          Let's work together to refine and elevate your brand, creating a
          lasting impression that resonates with your audience.
        </Text>
        <div class="flex mt-4">
          <Link size="xl" variant="default" href="/forms/contact">
            Contact us
          </Link>
        </div>
      </Wrapper>
    </section>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
